            </pg-code> -->
            <statement>
              <p>
                Show, using the definition of the Cross Product,
                that <m>\vec u\times\vec u=\vec 0</m>.
              </p>
            </statement>
            <solution>
              <p>
                With <m>\vec u = \la u_1,u_2,u_3\ra</m>, we have
                <md>
                  <mrow>\vec u\times\vec u \amp = \la u_2u_3-u_3u_2,-(u_1u_3-u_3u_1),u_1u_2-u_2u_1\ra)</mrow>
                  <mrow>\amp = \la 0,0,0\ra</mrow>
                  <mrow>\amp =\vec 0</mrow>
                </md>.
              </p>
            </solution>
        <!-- </webwork> -->
